00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:50,330
Pero hindi ko akalain na makakasagabal ako sayo dito.

221
00:14:50,330 --> 00:14:53,170
Na-assign ako pabalik sa head office.

222
00:14:53,170 --> 00:14:56,020
